<aura:component extends="auradocs:topicPanel">
    <aura:set attribute="title" value="Getting User Input" />
    <p>Aura provides out-of-the-box input components that enables you to easily retrieve and process user input with features such as value binding and event handling.
    </p>

    <h3><code>ui:input</code></h3>
    <p> <code>ui:input</code> is an abstract and extensible component that gets user input for processing. This component provides the attributes and events for all other child input components like
    <code>ui:inputText</code> and <code>ui:inputNumber</code>.</p>
    <auradocs:info>See the <auradocs:defLink descriptor ="ui:input">ui:input</auradocs:defLink> component reference.</auradocs:info>

